'''''Fox''''' was a [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|Nebulon-B escort frigate]] in the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. It was destroyed at the [[Battle of the Bajic Shipyards]].

==Behind the scenes==
It is possible to save the ''Fox'' in the game, but the player has to be willing to destroy the Imperial warships in order to do this.

